<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Parental Guidance - CareerGuide</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("header.ejs") %>

  <main class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="page-header">
        <h1>Parental Guidance</h1>
        <p>Supporting your child in making informed career decisions</p>
      </section>

      <section class="intro-section">
        <p class="intro-text">
          As a parent, you play a crucial role in your child's career decisions. Your guidance, support, and understanding can make a significant difference in their journey. Here are some resources to help you guide your child effectively.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="resources-section">
        <div class="resources-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h2>Understanding Modern Career Paths</h2>
            <p>Learn about the evolving job market and emerging career opportunities for your child.</p>
            <ul class="resource-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Overview of traditional and emerging careers</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Future job market trends</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Skills that will be in demand</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="resource-link">Learn more <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>

          <div class="resource-card">
            <h2>Supporting Your Child's Career Decisions</h2>
            <p>Tips on how to guide your child without imposing your own preferences.</p>
            <ul class="resource-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Effective communication strategies</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Balancing guidance with independence</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Handling disagreements constructively</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="resource-link">Learn more <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>

          <div class="resource-card">
            <h2>Balancing Academics and Extracurricular Activities</h2>
            <p>Strategies for helping your child develop a well-rounded profile.</p>
            <ul class="resource-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Importance of extracurricular activities</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Time management techniques</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Identifying meaningful activities</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="resource-link">Learn more <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>

          <div class="resource-card">
            <h2>Financial Planning for Higher Education</h2>
            <p>Information on scholarships, education loans, and saving strategies.</p>
            <ul class="resource-list">
                education loans, and saving strategies.</p>
            <ul class="resource-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Overview of scholarship opportunities</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Education loan options and considerations</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Long-term saving strategies</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="resource-link">Learn more <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reminder-section">
        <div class="reminder-card">
          <h2>Remember</h2>
          <ul class="reminder-list">
            <li>Every child is unique and may have different interests and aptitudes.</li>
            <li>Encourage exploration of various career paths.</li>
            <li>Focus on your child's strengths and passions rather than societal pressures.</li>
            <li>Stay informed about current educational and career trends.</li>
            <li>Seek professional career counseling if needed.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="parent-workshops">
        <h2>Parent Workshops</h2>
        <p>Join our upcoming workshops designed specifically for parents to help you better support your child's career journey.</p>
        <div class="workshops-grid">
          <div class="workshop-card">
            <div class="workshop-date">
              <span class="month">JUN</span>
              <span class="day">15</span>
            </div>
            <div class="workshop-details">
              <h3>Understanding Your Child's Aptitude</h3>
              <p>Learn how to identify and nurture your child's natural talents and interests.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-small">Register</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="workshop-card">
            <div class="workshop-date">
              <span class="month">JUL</span>
              <span class="day">10</span>
            </div>
            <div class="workshop-details">
              <h3>Navigating College Admissions</h3>
              <p>A comprehensive guide to the college application and admission process.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-small">Register</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include("footer.ejs") %>

  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

